data.code:
select 
    *
from (    
    SELECT 
        rc.rc_number,
        rc.company_name,
        rc.company_code,
        rc.order_number1,
        rc.order_type1,
        rc.woo_ref,
        rc.user_name,
        rc.poh_Auto_key,
        rc.roh_auto_key,
        rc.pod_auto_key,
        rc.rod_auto_key,
        rc.PN,
        rc.serial_number,
        rc.pn_desc,
        woo.wo_type,
        rc.receive_date,
        si_number,
        consignment_code,
        disp_code,
        rc.original_po_number,
        (
            case 
                when woo_ref is not null then row_number() over (partition by woo_ref order by receive_date ) 
                else 1 
            end 
        ) as l
    FROM (
        SELECT 
            rc_number,
            cmp.company_name,
            cmp.company_code,
            order_number1,
            order_type1,
            NVL(rch.woo_auto_key, rcd.woo_auto_key) AS woo_ref,
            rcs.serial_number as serial_number,
            sysur.user_name,
            rch.poh_Auto_key,
            rch.roh_auto_key,
            rcd.pod_auto_key,
            rcd.rod_auto_key,
            pnm.PN,
            pnm.description AS pn_desc,
            rch.entry_date AS receive_date,
            cnc.consignment_code,
            rdc.disp_code,
            stk.original_po_number
        FROM 
            rc_header rch
            INNER JOIN rc_detail rcd ON rch.rch_Auto_key = rcd.rch_auto_key
            left join rc_serial rcs on rcs.rcd_auto_key = rcd.rcd_auto_key
            left join stock stk on rcd.rcd_auto_key = stk.rcd_auto_key
            LEFT JOIN companies cmp ON rch.cmp_auto_key = cmp.cmp_auto_key
            LEFT JOIN sys_users sysur ON rch.sysur_auto_key = sysur.sysur_auto_key
            LEFT JOIN parts_master pnm ON rcd.pnm_auto_key = pnm.pnm_auto_key
            LEFT JOIN consignment_codes cnc ON rcd.cnc_auto_key = cnc.cnc_auto_key
            LEFT JOIN RC_DISP_CODES rdc ON rcd.rdc_Auto_key = rdc.rdc_Auto_key
    ) rc LEFT JOIN wo_operation woo ON rc.woo_ref = woo.woo_auto_key    
)
where
    l = 1     
    and (si_number not like '%-%' or si_number is null)
